  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1050">
<l>tuppura villār tuvarat tuṟavāmai</l>
<l>yuppiṟkuṅ kāṭikkuṅ kūṟṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The destitute poor, who do not renounce their bodies, only consume their neighbour's salt and water.</l>
            </lg>
